Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}红莲的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「顶之座」——赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,率领「扮装舞会」的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把悠二还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为容器已经结合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她就是被这庞大的存在之力所充满的机关的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒她就能停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然除了阻止「顶之座」以外别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽快 这样下去城市会崩坏也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎市会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…得做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的思念正充满着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今以来不知结合了多少容器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把欲望全部吞噬也未曾得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要去赫卡特那了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再陪我打一会是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（继续战斗）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真缠人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切…燃料过多也挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  看来会永远打下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「千变」啊 这难道不是你们的目的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要…我的赫卡特能满足就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳…变态的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是玩人偶的料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 一定能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对的 阪井同学和小紫一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不能靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把阪井悠二从那里放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把零时迷子分离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的都应该会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用我的记忆和思念来充满自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在追寻着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触摸到你的时候终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我追寻着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是单纯的火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是单纯的火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阪井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所追寻的是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真实存在着的…我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实…容器最初重合的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是空无一物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如此得被填满着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是我的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算用别人的回忆来填满自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的你并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是作为火炬的你不也被阪井悠二的回忆所充满着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 与夏娜相遇的我果然只是个单纯的火炬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时就一直在思考着 苦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来的那些都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以再明确地说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是阪井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于你的自己究竟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,填满我的东西…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会被我的回忆填满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从一开始就始终空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…有人拜托我要带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人和…吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在担心我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  最想这么做的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从一开始就始终空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不是说好不能中途退出的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（异常事态）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「顶之座」正在将吞噬了的存在之力释放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这量…真是恐怖的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此庞大的存在之力回流的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕已经没空等着自然恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多~~~么精彩的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻觉还是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是超越了世界所能承受界限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力的饱和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是待会要确认的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有唯一的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天壤之劫火」阿拉斯拖鲁的显现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显现？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是让阿拉斯拖鲁出现在这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为红世魔人的我的显现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会消耗大量的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要使用现在饱和的庞大存在之力来显现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计城市崩坏也会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果我显现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为容器的火焰之雾也会被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经便是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏是指…难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…会死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是炎发灼眼的火焰之雾被赐予的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全明白了这些才和阿拉斯拖鲁订下契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不好的预感是也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（急速前进）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为夏娜救了悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要作为火焰之雾来完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阪井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没时间带你逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和夏娜一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份心情现在也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天破壤碎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…喜欢悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（天破壤碎）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO~~~难得的饱和状态啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要着手准备下一个实验了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被「天壤之劫火」吞没的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的容器容纳了我的全部存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然订契约的时候我已经感觉到大小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 以后随时都可以出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话 赌上生命的行为怎么能一直尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原来还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也总算活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你干吗看别处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是夏娜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦罗嗦罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.55,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是走狗屎运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:08.46,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,你有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:09.63,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.06,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那 准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.61,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微离开下就这副德行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:15.07,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.16,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,在照看下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:25.10,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:27.30,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~别转了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:28.85,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊两位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:30.08,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.99,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐说暂时待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:34.40,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道好还是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:35.51,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:37.80,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能老实一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:00.40,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:03.74,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜 今天晚饭会准备好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:04.80,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:29.21,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:31.74,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:37.63,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:42.79,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,第二学期胜负会分晓也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 池
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天第二回合开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:23:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带悠二回来的时候还哭着道谢的说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说那是第一回合
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此加油吧 小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将来也会一成不变的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.74,0:24:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到在世界脱轨之前
